    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ari just wanted extra credit. Instead, he became the accidental wingman in a time-traveling heist to help his physics professor woo the history teacher.<strong> Perfect for Controllers and Steam Deck!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184020/extras/55baf7b1ac499e7108f49a6d8ad7d16a.poster.avif?t=1772127952\" width=780 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184020/extras/55baf7b1ac499e7108f49a6d8ad7d16a.webm?t=1772127952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184020/extras/55baf7b1ac499e7108f49a6d8ad7d16a.mp4?t=1772127952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184020/extras/7e669bfeec47f1ca3487cf957a8b296d.webp?t=1772127952\" width=450 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>LIFTED</strong></i> channels the spirit of classic adventure games, mixing wholesome platforming with high-stakes discovery. Follow clues to find the lost Tiara, solve environmental puzzles, and master fluid movement. Professor Raventhorpe provides the &quot;Vision&quot; while you provide the manual labor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184020/extras/2f55f47d4ca94ebdf8683c9ac7ebdfac.avif?t=1772127952\" width=500 height=304 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > But keep your head on a swivel. When the villains show up (or an avalanche starts), the pace explodes. The only way out is <i>through</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184020/extras/c5f7789c0ef8d34231f0595c50ce056e.webp?t=1772127952\" width=450 height=43 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184020/extras/a2270ef10eb65ec217424c6459e8ead9.poster.avif?t=1772127952\" width=780 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184020/extras/a2270ef10eb65ec217424c6459e8ead9.webm?t=1772127952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184020/extras/a2270ef10eb65ec217424c6459e8ead9.mp4?t=1772127952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Professor Raventhorpe’s &quot;Anytime Elevator&quot; hurtles you through both time AND space. In this machine, the floor numbers map to history.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hit the button for Floor 1712, align the map to the Caribbean, and you arrive in the Year 1712. Right in the middle of pirate-infested Tortuga! But watch out: while the Elevator gets the <i>time</i> right, it rarely lands exactly <i>where</i> you expected. Prof. R is still working out the kinks...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184020/extras/a262417629f1c8649b6efc75b73aa199.webp?t=1772127952\" width=450 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184020/extras/2e7d46cf3ff5852de9be3c30bc95773d.poster.avif?t=1772127952\" width=780 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184020/extras/2e7d46cf3ff5852de9be3c30bc95773d.webm?t=1772127952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184020/extras/2e7d46cf3ff5852de9be3c30bc95773d.mp4?t=1772127952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a story full of heart, humor, and 80s movie magic featuring top-tier voice acting from Joe Gaudet as Ari, Ray O'Hare as Professor Raventhorpe, and Evan Widjaja as Julius.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Slacker:</strong> Ari just wants to go home.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Genius:</strong> Professor Raventhorpe will do anything for love.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Chinchilla:</strong> Julius is the only one who knows what he's doing.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184020/extras/c15ee9b8190eb38bfee26068d21927ef.webp?t=1772127952\" width=450 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thanks for stopping by! If you have a few minutes, give the FREE DEMO a try and experience the beginning of Ari’s adventure today.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184020/extras/c085b536534c7301ff47a4ef57561284.avif?t=1772127952\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184020/extras/36114e69027096f88060ff2be0299daf.avif?t=1772127952\" width=450 height=94 /></span></p>",
